  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "This port of Risky Challenge adds 34 more levels to the original 40. \"Gussun Oyoyo\" also incorporates touched up cutscenes with voice-overs as well as intermission screens between levels. It is a game that can be described as a cross between Tetris, Solomon's Key and Lemmings. The game is a conversion of the Irem's arcade machine from 1993.",
